name: iPhone 12
description: The iPhone 12 is equipped with an OLED panel with the same diagonal as its predecessor iPhone 11 - 6.1 inches. The resolution is higher: 2532x1170 pixels, so the pixel density is 460 per inch (Retina XDR). The image is really impressive.

name: iPhone 12 mini
description: In terms of performance, photo quality and display, the iPhone 12 mini is not inferior to the most expensive models in its series. Its only drawback is the shorter autonomous operation. If we have to compare this iPhone with the iPhone 12 Pro and Pro Max, then the shortcomings are immediately apparent: the lack of a telephoto lens, an impractical rear surface, and others.

name: iPhone 12 Pro
description: Many Apple fans will appreciate the iPhone 12 Pro, as this model closely resembles the fourth and fifth generation iPhones. Compared to them, of course, it is much more technologically advanced. It offers a lot of modern features. Its dimensions have not changed in practice, but the screen diagonal is larger.

name: iphone 12 Pro Max
description: The iPhone 12 Pro Max is a large iPhone, with which you will have to work with both hands to enjoy it to the fullest. On its huge screen you will be happy to work with any content. The good news is that Apple engineers have tried to improve battery life.

name: iPhone SE
description: The 2020 iPhone SE is a modern device that doesn't elicit much excitement, but offers stable features and relevance for years to come.

name: iPhone 13
description: The iPhone 13 is an excellent representative of the Apple family. It will meet all user expectations. There is no other device of this type on the market with the same screen diagonal and performance.

name: iPhone 13 mini
description: The iPhone 13 mini is a continuation of the 12 mini from last year. It is the perfect solution if you need a compact smartphone. It is not inferior to its brothers in productivity and self-employment. The slot above the screen has gotten smaller, the cameras are just as good, and you've got plenty of memory for your favorite photos, videos, and music.

name: iPhone 13 Pro
description: The iPhone 13 Pro is a flagship device that has received a set of new sensors in the main camera, significantly improved battery life, and a display that supports a 120Hz refresh rate.

name: iPhone 13 Pro Max
description: It is a worthy representative of the Apple family. It will conquer you with its powerful platform of low consumption, its perfect screen and its impeccable design. It is also protected against humidity and dust according to the IP68 standard, it has wonderful cameras and you will be amazed at the quality of the videos. Self-employment complements the good impression.
